$\sum{F_y}=\mu dx\frac{\partial^2 y}{\partial t^2}$

\noindent 
$\sum{F_y}=T\frac{\partial y_2}{\partial x_2}-T\frac{\partial y_1}{\partial x_1}$

\noindent
$T\frac{
\frac{\partial y_2}{\partial x_2}-
\frac{\partial y_1}{\partial x_1}
 }{dx}=
\mu\frac{\partial^2 y}{\partial t^2}$

\noindent 
$T\frac{\partial^2 y}{\partial x^2}=
\mu\frac{\partial^2 y}{\partial t^2}$
